It specializes in providing air charter services by operating a unique fleet of ten Antonov An-124 (largest production cargo aircraft) and five IL-76TD-90VD (Stage IV) ramp all cargo aircraft certified for global operations. It is a world leader in the global market for the movement of oversize, unique and heavy air cargo.[1] "Volga-Dnepr Airlines" serves governmental and commercial organizations, including leading global businesses in the oil and gas, energy, aerospace, agriculture and telecommunications industries as well as the humanitarian and emergency services sectors.
